<ns2920:section xmlns:ns2920="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="resources.information.concepts.architecture.mda.introduction.currentProblems">

  <ns2921:title xmlns:ns2921="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Problems currently experienced</ns2921:title>
  <ns2922:para xmlns:ns2922="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    One of the core problems often experienced is that <ns2923:emphasis xmlns:ns2923="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">as technologies change, 
    large parts of one's architecture and design need to change</ns2923:emphasis>. Furthermore, 
    it may not be clear which parts need to be revisited and which parts remain constant.
  </ns2922:para>
  <ns2924:para xmlns:ns2924="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    As such, <ns2925:emphasis xmlns:ns2925="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">migration across technologies is expensive and disruptive</ns2925:emphasis>.
  </ns2924:para>
</ns2920:section>